import React from "react"
import '../../assets/css/Busquedas.css';

import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form'
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col'
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row'
import Card from 'react-bootstrap/Card'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'

function FormBusqueda(){

  return(
    <Card>
      <Card.Header id='card_header'>Busqueda de preguntas en la BBDD</Card.Header>
      <Card.Body class="card-body d-flex flex-column" id='busqueda_card_body'>
        <Container fluid='true'>
          <Row top="xs">
            <Col md={6}>
              <Form.Control placeholder="Asignatura" id='form_element'/>
                <Form.Control placeholder="Asignatura" id='form_element'/>
            </Col>
            <Col>
              <Form.Control placeholder="Asignatura" id='form_element'/>
            </Col>
          </Row>
          <Row mt-auto>
            <Button id='standard_button'>Buscar</Button>
          </Row>
        </Container>
      </Card.Body>
    </Card>

  )
}

export default FormBusqueda
